{"id": "1426415690298032188", "channel_id": "1426405667823947817", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "Yes, still Arc 1 rule. However, the scoring rules will be simplified to focus on difficulty first and then the number of rounds. Dreamspark and Dreamshard can be exchanged for D-Jewel, with a weekly limit. D-Jewel will be obtainable through weekly trial tasks.", "timestamp": "2025-10-11T03:46:42.089000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["436851757260341250"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "celeste_wish", "emoji_id": "1333977832791085107", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1426412754520113162", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1426405667823947817", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：V2.4 幻梦深潜与相位对弈生涯奖励重做 Preview: V2.4 Phantasmal Dive and Traphase Career Rewards Rework", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
